game.name: Frozen Baby Bedtime Caring
game.description:
It is time to sleep for the lovely and cute frozen baby sisters! Yes, the cute babies of Disney princesses Anna and Elsa want to go to bed and enjoy a wonderful sleep. But, they are unable to change their dresses since they are too small. These cute kids need the help of someone. Would you show off your fabulous fashion designer abilities to help them to pick up the night clothes fast? Join Frozen Baby Bedtime Caring game and prove the world that your baby carrying skills are enough to handle this task!

Your objective in this brand new dressing game for girls is to help babies to pick up some good-looking yet comfortable pajamas and other things they need to have before going to bed. Over the screen, you will spot plenty of objects which will be enough to make their bedtime easier. Make sure that you feed them timely before they start crying and also play to a lullaby for them. These both sisters rely on you, so do your best to help their babies fall asleep. 

Apart from guiding them to choose the matching and comfortable pajamas, make sure that you implement all the things required to make them feel happy. It will be in your hands now how to take care of these two little kids and allow them to have a good night with their beloved mothers. Change their hairstyles, pajamas, and shocks in this dress-up mobile game! Find all the needful objects then to make their bedtime comfortable! Enjoy with these super cute kids online on atmegame.com, no download required!
